I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife.

transcription: {"text": "So, the girl you've been on a few dates with stops responding, leaving you to wonder one thing. Why? If you're like most guys, you wait a few days, text her again, and she responds, I'm just not really into dating right now. But did you ever stop to wonder why this keeps happening to you? The truth is, she just isn't that into you. If your dates aren't getting more and more intimate, it's simply a matter of time before she either axes you or puts you in the friend zone. And if you haven't kissed her within the first few hours, odds are you never will. So if you're dating a girl right now, but things aren't getting sexual, the reason is simple. There isn't enough sexual tension. Sexual tension is the key. It's the one ingredient that makes her obsessed and completely open up to you both physically and emotionally. Think about it. There's already natural tension between men and women. It's the same tension you feel when you're walking past a girl on the sidewalk, or when you're trying to order a drink standing at the bar next to her. When you're on a date, the tension is already there. She wouldn't show up if she wasn't attracted to you. So all you have to do is direct that tension into action. And if you've been taking girls out to fancy dinners or on extravagant activities before even kissing her, you're actually killing the tension and placing yourself in the friend zone. Robby Kramer here. I'm a dating coach, founder of Inner Confidence, and The Leverage Podcast. I specialize in helping guys who work in IT and entrepreneurs take a scientific approach to their dating life to optimize the entire process. I'm a pretty average-looking guy, but I've dated women that most guys drool over, and I recently married a Miss Ukraine finalist. And this is the lifestyle I lived before marrying her, partying on yachts with Playboy models, doing things so cool that they didn't even seem real. But before I figured this stuff out, I lived in the friend zone. I didn't really have a problem talking to women I wasn't super attracted to, but I wanted the top of the top, and I always felt like I was settling. After watching a girl I was totally obsessed with hook up with one of my friends, I decided to make it my mission to figure this stuff out. So to make sure nothing like this ever happens to you, click the link to watch the next video. I created a system called the Social Funnel Method, and it's the easiest and fastest way to attract model-quality women, even if you're not tall, rich, or handsome. But if everyone starts using the system, it's going to lose its effectiveness, so I'm only sharing the system for a short period of time. If you want to learn exactly how this system works, I created a free video that breaks everything down. I'm not selling anything here. When you watch this video, you'll see exactly how I went from being lonely on the weekends to hooking up with girls with millions of followers. Click the link, and I'll see you in the next video.
